data.description: ** OPEN HOUSE SUN 2/4 12-3 PM **Modern, move-in ready home nestled in the charming Beacon Hill neighborhood! Inviting open floor plan with hand-scraped birch floors, tall ceilings and designer details throughout. Well appointed kitchen with Kitchen Aid appliances, large island with breakfast bar, dual sinks, walk-in pantry, and tile backsplash overlooking the dining area and sunny living room. Upstairs, the primary bedroom with its vaulted ceilings, adds an extra layer of sophistication to this home's design with an attached ensuite bath is a true sanctuary, boasting quartz vanity, walk-in shower and spacious closet. Outside, the unique open concept garage and front covered deck makes relaxing and entertaining effortless. Property is also available for rent.
